<doc id="938270" wikidata="Q5559261" url="?curid=938270" title="Gibson, Louisiana">
<text>Gibson is an unincorporated community in Terrebonne Parish, Louisiana, United States. The zip code is 70356. It is part of the Houma–Bayou Cane–Thibodaux Metropolitan Statistical Area.

==Geography==
Gibson is located at , on LA Highway 182 between Houma and Morgan City.

==Education==
Terrebonne Parish School District operates public schools. Gibson Elementary School is located in the community.

Terrebonne Parish Public Library operates the Gibson Branch.

