*&quot;Marie&#x27;s story. A tale of the days of Louis XIV.&quot;. Congregational S.S. &amp; Pub. Soc. (1888)
*&quot;Miss Millie&#x27;s Trying&quot;. Hunt &amp; Eaton. (1892)
*&quot;Number One or Number Two&quot;. Hunt &amp; Eaton. (1891)
